data.description: Don’t miss your chance at this 3/bed 3/ bath home sitting on over an acre in Warren Local School District. This home offers a large wrap-around porch overlooking the valley. Attached oversized two-stall garage with electricity and water. Inside you will find a large master suite. Large, finished walkout basement with bedroom as well as a bathroom. This home is a charmer and ready for its new owners for the holidays! Call for your showing today! ***Seller is willing to contribute to buyers closing cost***
